---
// 退会前アップセル専用ページ
// クライアントサイドで日付計算（デプロイ不要）
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>退会前にご確認ください - KEIBA Analytics</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      padding: 2rem;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .upsell-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 3rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #f59e0b;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      color: #10b981;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .hit-image {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 700px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      margin: 2rem auto;
      display: block;
      border: 2px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    }

    .description {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .description strong {
      color: #fbbf24;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .price-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ef4444);
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    }

    .badge-discount {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #fff;
      color: #ef4444;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .original-price {
      text-decoration: line-through;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .sale-price {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .price-note {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .button-group {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta-button {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.6);
    }

    .secondary-button {
      background: transparent;
      border: 2px solid #64748b;
      color: #94a3b8;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: inherit;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .secondary-button:hover {
      border-color: #e2e8f0;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      background: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.1);
    }

    .highlight-box {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .highlight-box p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #60a5fa;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* 痛みポイント・解決策セクション */
    .pain-section {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
    }

    .pain-item,
    .solution-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .pain-item:hover {
      border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.5);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    }

    .solution-item {
      background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
      border: 2px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.5);
    }

    .solution-item:hover {
      border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.7);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
    }

    .pain-icon,
    .solution-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .pain-text strong,
    .solution-text strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .solution-text strong {
      color: #10b981;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .pain-text p,
    .solution-text p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .solution-text p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    /* お客様の声（社会的証明） */
    .testimonial {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
      border-left: 4px solid #fbbf24;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .testimonial-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .testimonial-author {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* 緊急性警告 */
    .urgency-warning {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1), rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1));
      border: 2px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.5);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fbbf24;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .upsell-container {
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }

      .title {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .description {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .sale-price {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      .cta-button {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
      }

      .pain-section {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .pain-item,
      .solution-item {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.8rem;
        padding: 1.2rem;
      }

      .pain-icon,
      .solution-icon {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .pain-text strong,
      .solution-text strong {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .testimonial {
        padding: 1.2rem;
      }

      .testimonial-text {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .urgency-warning {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .urgency-warning p {
        font-size: 0.9rem !important;
      }
    }

    /* ========================================
       銀行振込モーダル
       ======================================== */
    .bank-modal {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        z-index: 9999;
        overflow-y: auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .bank-modal.active {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .bank-modal-content {
        position: relative;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.98) 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98) 100%);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 40px;
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 40px auto;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .bank-modal-close {
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
        color: #ef4444;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .bank-modal-close:hover {
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.6);
        transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .bank-modal-title {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #60a5fa;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .modal-plan-info {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #fbbf24;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .bank-info-box {
        background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .bank-info-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 12px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.1);
    }

    .bank-info-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .bank-info-label {
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.7);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .bank-info-value {
        color: #e2e8f0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
    }

    .copy-button {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
        border: none;
        color: white;
        padding: 6px 12px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .copy-button:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    }

    .bank-steps {
        background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .bank-steps-title {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #60a5fa;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .bank-step {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.9);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .bank-step:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .bank-step-number {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
        color: white;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .bank-form-section {
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .bank-form-title {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #60a5fa;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .bank-form {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .form-group {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
    }

    .form-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .form-label {
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.9);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .required {
        color: #ef4444;
    }

    .form-input {
        background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        color: #e2e8f0;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .form-input:focus {
        outline: none;
        border-color: #3b82f6;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    }

    .form-hint {
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.6);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .form-submit-button {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
        border: none;
        color: white;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .form-submit-button:hover:not(:disabled) {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
    }

    .form-submit-button:disabled {
        opacity: 0.6;
        cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .form-message {
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .form-message.success {
        background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
        color: #10b981;
    }

    .form-message.error {
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
        color: #ef4444;
    }

    .bank-warning {
        background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .bank-warning-title {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #f59e0b;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .bank-warning-text {
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="upsell-container">
    <h1 class="title">退会を考えられた理由、<br>わかります。</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">でも、その悩みを解決する方法があります。</p>

    <!-- 退会理由への共感セクション -->
    <div class="pain-section">
      <h3 style="color: #fbbf24; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">😰 こんな理由で退会を考えていませんか？</h3>

      <div class="pain-item">
        <span class="pain-icon">❌</span>
        <div class="pain-text">
          <strong>3つの戦略、結局どれを選べばいいか分からない</strong>
          <p>少点数的中型？バランス型？高配当追求型？毎回悩んでしまう...</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pain-item">
        <span class="pain-icon">❌</span>
        <div class="pain-text">
          <strong>オッズを確認して戦略を選ぶのが面倒</strong>
          <p>11倍以上なら○○型、11倍以下なら△△型...毎回調べるのが大変</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pain-item">
        <span class="pain-icon">❌</span>
        <div class="pain-text">
          <strong>毎レースチェックする時間がない</strong>
          <p>12レース全部見て、3戦略を比較検討...時間がいくらあっても足りない</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="solution-item">
        <span class="solution-icon">✅</span>
        <div class="solution-text">
          <strong>プレミアムプラスなら、これらの悩みをすべて解決</strong>
          <p>超精密AIが選んだ1鞍だけ。選択の悩みゼロ、時間不要、届いた買い目を購入するだけ。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 実績セクション -->
    <h3 style="color: #10b981; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem; text-align: center;">📊 実際の的中実績をご覧ください</h3>

    <img
      id="hitImage"
      src=""
      alt="実際の的中実績 - AI超精密買い目"
      class="hit-image"
      loading="eager"
    />

    <div class="description">
      <p>
        <strong>三連単少点数</strong>で、<strong style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fbbf24;">平均配当¥281,340</strong>を実現。
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        的中率<strong>78%</strong>、期待リターン<strong>265%</strong>（投資額の約2.7倍回収）を記録。
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        これは<strong>AIにしか実現できない</strong>、数万通りの買い目から厳選した超精密買い目です。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 解決策セクション -->
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p>
        <strong>1日1鞍限定・AI超精密買い目</strong>を提供する<br>
        <strong>「プレミアムプラス」プラン</strong>を、<br>
        退会者様限定<strong>50%OFF（¥19,000引き）</strong>でご案内します。
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #94a3b8;">
        数万通りの買い目からAIが導き出す、<br>
        「最高確率の1鞍」だけを厳選配信。選択不要、時間不要。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 社会的証明セクション -->
    <div class="testimonial">
      <p class="testimonial-text">
        「退会を考えていましたが、プレミアムプラスに変えて正解でした。
        投資額は1/3になり、的中率は逆に上がりました。
        選択のストレスがなくなって、競馬が純粋に楽しめるようになりました。」
      </p>
      <p class="testimonial-author">— 40代男性・会社員</p>
    </div>

    <div class="price-box">
      <div class="badge-discount">🎯 ラストチャンス 🎯</div>
      <div class="sale-price">¥68,000</div>
      <p class="price-note">
        ※次の超勝負レース1鞍のAI超精密買い目提供<br>
        ※人間では実現不可能なレベルの的中精度
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ラストチャンス強調 -->
    <div class="urgency-warning">
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        ⚠️ この割引コードは、このページからのお申し込み限定です
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #cbd5e1;">
        一度退会されますと、この特別割引で再度ご利用いただくことはできません。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="button-group">
      <button onclick="openBankModal(\'Premium Plus\', 68000)" class="cta-button">
        🏦 銀行振込で申し込む
      </a>

      <button id="proceedWithdrawal" class="secondary-button">
        いいえ、退会手続きに進む
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- 退会確認モーダル -->
    <div id="withdrawalModal" style="display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); z-index: 9999; overflow-y: auto;">
      <div style="background: #1e293b; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 500px; margin: 2rem auto; position: relative;">
        <h3 style="color: #f87171; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">本当に退会しますか？</h3>
        <p style="color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          退会理由を教えてください。
        </p>

        <textarea id="withdrawalReason" placeholder="退会理由" style="width: 100%; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; background: #0f172a; color: #e2e8f0; border: 1px solid #334155; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; min-height: 100px; font-family: inherit;"></textarea>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
          <button id="confirmWithdrawal" style="flex: 1; padding: 1rem; background: #ef4444; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer;">
            退会する
          </button>
          <button id="cancelWithdrawal" style="flex: 1; padding: 1rem; background: #334155; color: #e2e8f0; border: none; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer;">
            キャンセル
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
